{"tid":1236434,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"因為黑警既關係 搞到今日同條女扑野都扑唔順利","createTime":"2019-06-17T12:11:01.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-17T14:24:27.000Z","uid":7043,"like":6,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"cfb843cab7d834eb78a90caf8137e8cf04e9b127","tid":1236434,"uid":7043,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T12:11:01.000Z","msg":"今日見到條女又有d緊火<br />\n就啦啦聲扑下啦<br />\n咩前戲咩樣靚波甜個d唔係重點就唔講啦<br />\n後入緊個陣<br />\n見到佢個粉嫩屎眼咪拎隻手指挑逗下<br />\n點知佢講左句<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">唔好搞我後面</span></span><br />\n唉屌呢句野搞到我即時聯想到死黑警有幻覺個個畫面<br />\n之後我隻小天王就失去左硬化形態<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n條女見到仲以為我唔搞後面唔得<br />\n之後仲俾佢串最多俾你搞後面啦死變態<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">屌你老母死黑警搞到我變左變態</span></span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bbf987b7a32526265daa474639a6c1b3b34b9b8f","tid":1236434,"uid":32577,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T12:18:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />gay"},{"pid":"fe6f2f676e4fdd6e22819a57cf99a39262445043","tid":1236434,"uid":152432,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T12:19:47.000Z","msg":"gay<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a086b1bef7cab91450f756dbbfc84882bd9a1250","tid":1236434,"uid":7043,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"bbf987b7a32526265daa474639a6c1b3